<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>QR Code - <%= vehicle.licensePlate %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/vehicles" class="nav-brand">üö® AssistQR</a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/vehicles/<%= vehicle.id %>" class="nav-link">‚Üê Back to Vehicle</a>
                <span class="nav-user">Hello, <%= user.name %></span>
                <a href="/auth/logout" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Logout</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container-sm">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h1 class="card-title">QR Code for <%= vehicle.licensePlate %></h1>
                <p>Print or save this QR code and place it on your vehicle</p>
            </div>

            <div class="qr-container">
                <img src="<%= qrCodeDataUrl %>" alt="QR Code" class="qr-image">
                <p style="margin: 1rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                    Anyone scanning this QR code will be able to report an accident involving this vehicle.
                </p>
                <div class="d-flex gap-2" style="justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <a href="<%= downloadUrl %>" class="btn btn-primary" download>Download QR Code</a>
                    <button onclick="window.print()" class="btn btn-outline">Print QR Code</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Instructions:</h3>
                <ol style="line-height: 2; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                    <li>Download or print this QR code</li>
                    <li>Laminate it for weather protection</li>
                    <li>Place it in a visible location on your vehicle (dashboard, rear window, or side panel)</li>
                    <li>When scanned, it will allow bystanders to report accidents and notify your emergency contacts</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1rem; background-color: #fff3cd; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #ffc107;">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #856404;">
                    <strong>Privacy Note:</strong> The QR code only contains a secure token. 
                    It does not reveal any personal information, phone numbers, or email addresses.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        @media print {
            @page {
                size: A4;
                margin: 1cm;
            }
            
            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }
            
            .navbar, .btn, nav, .d-flex { 
                display: none !important; 
            }
            
            .card { 
                box-shadow: none; 
                border: none;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0;
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
            
            .card-header {
                padding: 0.5rem 0;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            }
            
            .card-header h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
            }
            
            .card-header p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                margin: 0;
            }
            
            .qr-container {
                text-align: center;
                padding: 0.5rem 0;
            }
            
            .qr-image { 
                max-width: 60%;
                max-height: 400px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
            
            .qr-container p {
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                margin: 0.5rem 0;
            }
            
            /* Instructions section - compact for print */
            div[style*="margin-top: 2rem"] {
                margin-top: 0.75rem !important;
                padding-top: 0.75rem !important;
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
            
            h3 {
                font-size: 1rem;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
            }
            
            ol {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                line-height: 1.4 !important;
                margin: 0.5rem 0;
                padding-left: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            /* Privacy note - make it smaller and compact */
            div[style*="background-color: #fff3cd"] {
                margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
                padding: 0.5rem !important;
                font-size: 0.75rem !important;
                page-break-inside: avoid;
            }
            
            /* Ensure everything fits on one page */
            .container-sm {
                max-width: 100%;
                padding: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>

